                    <a href="/en/dep/ad/aktuelt/nyheter/2009/endringer-i-departementsstrukturen.html?id=589457" title="">
                        Changes in the ministry structure
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[31.12.2009]</p>
                <p>From 1 January 2010 the Norwegian ministry structure is changed. As a consequence, The Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion has transferred some departments to other Minstries, and changed its name to The Ministry of Labour. </p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
