                        International Migration 2007-2008
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[30.12.2008]</p>
                <p>Annually Norway sends a report to the OECD – Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development – as a contribution to the common reporting system on migration for the member countries, called SOPEMI. The recent report for Norway covers 2007 and to some extent 2008.</p>
                
                
