                        Norway restricts its practice concerning asylum seekers from Southern-Somalia
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[03.12.2008]</p>
                <p>The Ministry of Labour and Social Inclusion recently instructed the Norwegian Directorate of Immigration to change its practice concerning asylum seekers from Southern Somalia. The new practice is effective immediately.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
