            <div class="ArticleImgContent">
                <h2>
                    <a href="/en/dep/ad/pressesenter/pressemeldinger/2008/hurtighandsaming-av-irakiske-asylsoknade.html?id=536769" title="">
                        Fast track procedure for asylum applications from Iraqis
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[18.11.2008]</p>
                <p>The Government of Norway announced in September 2008 thirteen measures to decrease the numbers of asylum seekers to Norway without a need for protection. One of the measures was to establish a fast track procedure for particular groups with a high percentage of rejections. The Directorate of Migration (UDI) and the police has now established a fast track procedure in a transit reception centre in Torshov, Oslo. The Torshov project will process asylum applications from Iraqis that can be decided quickly.</p>
                
                
                <p>
                    
                    
                </p>
                                 
           </div>
        </div> 
    
