                <p class="ArticleInfo">[20.02.2008]</p>
                <p>A press release from the Norwegian Technical Calculation Committee for Wage Settlements (TBU) reveals that the average annual pay growth from 2006 to 2007 for all groups is estimated at 5.4 per cent.</p>
                
                
